Why This Matters

-   **Only app rewarding BOTH positive actions AND avoided negative
    actions**

-   Pure positive reinforcement---users never lose money, only earn

-   Daily RESIST habit detection creates continuous engagement

-   Real money transfers from day one---not a future feature

-   Behavioral indices create competitive advantage and data moat
